/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:512:- Fixed temporary extension package installs to use a private `~/.pi/agent/tmp/extensions` directory with `0700` permissions instead of `os.tmpdir()/pi-extensions`.
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:753:- Fixed user-scoped npm pi packages to install under `~/.pi/agent/npm/` instead of npm's global package root, avoiding permission errors with system-managed Node installs ([#4587](https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/issues/4587)).
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:1213:- Fixed skill resolution to dedupe symlinked aliases by canonical path, so `pi config` no longer shows duplicate skill entries when `~/.pi/agent/skills` points to `~/.agents/skills` ([#3417](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/3417) by [@rwachtler](https://github.com/rwachtler))
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:1309:- Fixed markdown strikethrough parsing in interactive rendering and HTML export to require strict double-tilde delimiters (`~~text~~`) with non-whitespace boundaries.
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:1605:- Fixed skill discovery to stop recursing once a directory contains `SKILL.md`, and to ignore root `*.md` files in `.agents/skills` while keeping root markdown skill files supported in `~/.pi/agent/skills`, `.pi/skills`, and package `skills/` directories ([#2603](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/2603))
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:1969:- Fixed `pi config` misclassifying `~/.agents/skills` as project-scoped in non-git directories under `$HOME`, so toggling those skills no longer writes project overrides to `.pi/settings.json` ([#1915](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/issues/1915))
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:2146:- Resource precedence for extensions, skills, prompts, themes, and slash-command name collisions is now project-first (`cwd/.pi`) before user-global (`~/.pi/agent`). If you relied on global resources overriding project resources with the same names, rename or reorder your resources.
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:2167:- Added default skill auto-discovery for `.agents/skills` locations. Pi now discovers project skills from `.agents/skills` in `cwd` and ancestor directories (up to git repo root, or filesystem root when not in a repo), and global skills from `~/.agents/skills`, in addition to existing `.pi` skill paths.
