/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:2830:- Fixed error messages showing hardcoded `~/.pi/agent/` paths instead of respecting `PI_CODING_AGENT_DIR` ([#887](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/887) by [@aliou](https://github.com/aliou))
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:2933:- Fixed `PI_CODING_AGENT_DIR` env var not expanding tilde (`~`) to home directory ([#778](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/778) by [@aliou](https://github.com/aliou))
/nix/store/df3vi9dd4pkywmr1b52a2kb9jv0w88kv-pi-0.80.7/libexec/pi/CHANGELOG.md:3348:- Managed binaries (`fd`, `rg`) now stored in `~/.pi/agent/bin/` instead of `tools/`, eliminating false deprecation warnings ([#470](https://github.com/badlogic/pi-mono/pull/470) by [@mcinteerj](https://github.com/mcinteerj))
